												<Text>
													<Options>10</Options>
													<StyledText>
														<Data><![CDATA[The recommended settings for duplicating a <<gCloneLevel>> are checked. This is what they do:- IOs Duplicate existing IOs within the <<gCloneLevel>> for all page items and lists. This will replace text variables too.- Links Duplicate existing Links within the <<gCloneLevel>>. Connect items with the new link for all page items and lists within the <<gCloneLevel>>. - Lists Duplicate existing Lists with new Lists. All page items and IOs within the <<gCloneLevel>> will use the new Lists.- Tags Duplicate existing Tags with new Tags and Lists for Tag filter. Creates new IO for tag filter too.- Score categories. Duplicate existing Score categories that are used within the <<gCloneLevel>>. New score categories will be used for all score condititions.- Score rewards Duplicate existing Score rewards that are used within the <<gCloneLevel>>- Localised texts Create new localised texts when duplicating - if any localised texts exists.]]></Data>
